<style>
  /* Container and typography styles */
  .marketing-div {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 40px 80px;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #000000;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .marketing-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #007bff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* List styling */
  .marketing-ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .marketing-ul li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .marketing-ul li b {
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Link styling */
  .marketing-ul a {
    color: #007bff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .marketing-ul a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Image styling */
  .marketing-ul img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin: 15px 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .marketing-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .marketing-div {
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .marketing-ul li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .marketing-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .marketing-div {
      margin: 20px 15px;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .marketing-ul li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .marketing-ul img {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>
<div class="marketing-div">
  <h3 class="marketing-title">HOW TO POST IN INDIA MART.</h3>
  <ul class="marketing-ul">
    <li><b>Step 1:</b> First sign in India MART using your phone number.</li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f1.png" alt="" />
    <li><b>Step 2:</b> It will ask for OTP.</li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f2.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 3:</b>Once you fill the OTP & click Verify, you are done with your
      registration. You can also edit your profile.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f3.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 4:</b> When you click on Edit Profile you will redirect to a page
      & fill all the required details.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f4.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 5:</b> Save all information. When you save the email section, an
      OTP will come on your phone number & on your email ID
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f5.png" alt="" />
    <img src="../images/marketing-f5a.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 6:</b>To start posting or selling your services click on Sell
      option
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f6.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 7:</b> Where you have again registered with the same details.
      Check the I agree to terms and privacy policy box & click on Register for
      Free. Then an OTP will come on your Mobile number again. Submit the OTP &
      hit the Continue button. You will redirect to a new page where you have to
      upload images related to your services.
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>Step 8:</b> Once you fill the all details continue, you are done with
      your posting & welcome screen will appear
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-f8.png" alt="" />
  </ul>
</div>
